public ServerFactory.ListenerControl listen(java.util.Map settings,
                                            ServerFactory.AcceptCallback cb)
Description copied from interface: ServerFactory
Bind a listener to receive client callbacks.

This call should return immediately; if a thread is required, the ServerFactory implementation must spawn its own background thread. Similarily, if client callbacks require a thread to avoid blocking other parallel callbacks, this ServerFactory implementation must spawn that thread.
